#summary Alegria Demo #1 page.

= Introduction =

Alegria Demo #1 will be the first game developed with the Alegria Engine. The idea behind it is to make a relatively small but complete game in order to add the needed features to the engine.


= Features Needed =

  * Sprite animation. (DONE)
  * Mouse support.  (DONE)
  * Dinamic Text.   (DONE)   
  * Messaging system. (DONE)
  * Particle system. (DONE)